  "text": "We notice that the results of our implemented ResNet on MXNet, and the results from [CITATION_1] are different. We also want to point out that the settings are the same with [CITATION_2] . We think that the difference might be from the MXNet platform, or there might be some other untested issues as pointed in https://github.com/KaimingHe/ deep-residual-networks. ",
